Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.42,0:38:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想這不是原子彈設計藍圖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, uh, I figure it's either a blueprint for the A-bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.62,0:39:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是杰姬送來的總統就職典禮邀請函\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or a Jackie sent in a personal invite to the swearing-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.50,0:39:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.70,0:39:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的競爭對手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's our competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.96,0:39:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加州大學洛杉磯分校的那個博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The doctor at U.C.L.A..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.50,0:39:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是他寫的書\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is his book.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.59,0:39:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別引人入勝嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A real page-turner?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.10,0:39:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容不多  也不深奧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's thin, conversational.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.80,0:39:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫給外行看的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's written for the layman.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.87,0:39:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有復雜的科學知識\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not much science.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.45,0:39:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有數據注釋  其實幾乎沒有數據\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No annotating of data -- hardly any data at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.12,0:39:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來更像是消遣讀物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hmm, more like summer reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.06,0:39:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我們拍的片子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}More like our film.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.32,0:39:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們的研究  我們真正的研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whereas our work -- our real work --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.88,0:39:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠不是科夫曼醫生所能及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is miles beyond Dr. Kaufman's.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.80,0:39:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的研究  會讓卡夫曼醫生被世人所遺忘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our work...will leave Dr. Kaufman in the dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.60,0:39:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.46,0:39:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前總會取笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I used to poke fun at your bow tie
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.54,0:39:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的領結\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the past, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.48,0:39:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他們在拍攝過程中讓你系的正規領帶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that regular tie they put you in for the filming --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.75,0:39:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你也并沒什么幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that wasn't doing you any favors, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.28,0:40:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.32,0:40:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不像你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.08,0:40:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在安排后續采訪的時間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I'm, uh, scheduling these follow-up interviews now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.43,0:40:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能否給你個建議  還是繼續用領結吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But may I suggest...stick with the bow tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.57,0:40:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信我會說出這種話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I cannot...believe I am saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.74,0:40:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會仔細考慮的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll take that under advisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.68,0:40:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得  我得跟你談談\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need to, uh -- I need to talk to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.37,0:40:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于咱們的片子  關于這份稿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}About our film... Uh, about, uh, this manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.96,0:40:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你談  一種可能性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to talk to you about a -- well, a-a possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.95,0:40:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗吉妮婭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Virginia?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.53,0:40:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.93,0:40:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等赫伯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, I'm waiting for Herb.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.24,0:41:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫伯是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who's Herb?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.32,0:41:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們的租戶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our tenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.47,0:41:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的律師\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.38,0:41:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你雇了赫伯·史普利博\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You hired Herb Spleeb?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.07,0:41:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.32,0:41:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我丈夫想要的東西給他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, to give my husband what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.16,0:41:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What does he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.03,0:41:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.97,0:41:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}George -- 
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.15,0:41:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他認為我是個不稱職的母親\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he wanted to put my fitness on trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.33,0:41:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要與我對簿公堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.85,0:41:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要讓大家都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He -- he wanted to make it a matter of public record
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.97,0:41:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的工作實質上淫亂不堪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the prurient nature of our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.98,0:41:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我在這里都干了什么  和你在一起時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the hours I spend here and the hours I spend...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.28,0:41:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都干了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.44,0:41:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯然他的律師已經開始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Apparently, his lawyer had already begun asking questions
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.00,0:41:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公園廣場酒店調查了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at the Park Plaza Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.08,0:41:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-喬治  -沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- George. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.14,0:41:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-喬治要這么做  -對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- George is doing this. - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.75,0:41:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味著我們會有兩次露面的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Meaning we would have had two debuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.80,0:41:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊是CBS  我們將作為開創性的研究者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One on CBS, the two of us being introduced to the country
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.66,0:41:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被世人所認識  與此同時  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as groundbreaking researchers, while at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.92,0:42:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個法庭的法官將會向世界宣布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a judge in some court would also be presenting us
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.63,0:42:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是一對道德淪喪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to the world as sleazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.27,0:42:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淫亂無恥的狗男女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}amoral smut peddlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.54,0:42:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能讓自己陷入那種境地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You -- you -- you cannot be put in that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.00,0:42:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗吉妮婭  那樣你根本沒有機會勝訴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Virginia, that's -- that's completely untenable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.41,0:42:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們要這么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So -- so what we do --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.48,0:42:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  我已經解決了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, no, no. It's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.66,0:42:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫伯這會兒正在向喬治提議\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Herb is presenting an offer to George as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.40,0:42:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出的條件對喬治來說非常有利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the terms are very favorable to George.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.67,0:42:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他同意這事不上法庭就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All he has to do is keep it out of court.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.22,0:42:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提議\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.19,0:42:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.55,0:42:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't, uh --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.92,0:42:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會放棄了孩子的撫養權吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't given up your children, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.54,0:42:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這么說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.78,0:42:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦影片播出后  我就能將他們奪回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But once the film airs, I will get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.67,0:42:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗吉妮婭  你不會真...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Virginia, you didn't do --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.46,0:42:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我會用這段影片證明這份工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I will use the film to show that this work --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.87,0:42:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這份工作的付出是實實在在  值得尊重的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that my part in our work is respectable and legitimate
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.87,0:42:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快有一天  我會將他拉上法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And one day, very soon, I will drag him into court
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.23,0:42:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后利用CBS的盛譽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I can use the sterling
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.41,0:42:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將孩子們奪回來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}reputation of CBS to get the kids back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.42,0:42:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你不能...  你現在就得將他們奪回來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, you cann-- no, you have to get them back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.48,0:43:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到  這已成事實了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. I can't. It's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.68,0:43:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是暫時的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's only temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.20,0:43:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.31,0:43:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.03,0:43:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道喬治·華盛頓特別喜歡狗嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you know George Washington really loved dogs a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.15,0:43:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他最喜歡的一只叫"甜嘴"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And his favorite one was named sweet lips?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.45,0:43:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.02,0:43:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你知道希臘曾經是一座島嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you know Greece was an island?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.36,0:43:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有個問題問你們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ooh, here's my question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.28,0:43:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們爸爸和我一直在商量一件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Um, your dad and I were talking about something
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.55,0:43:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們或許會感興趣的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that you might think is fun.
